{"type": "article", "id": 31098, "title": "Coty 集中力量开发高级香水，以及，推荐Porter的麂皮包袋系列 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-08-17T02:34:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 188, "name": "LV"}, {"id": 1936, "name": "香水"}, {"id": 2788, "name": "Band of Outsiders"}, {"id": 26421, "name": "Urban Decay"}, {"id": 31596, "name": "FAT"}, {"id": 3865, "name": "adidas Originals"}, {"id": 14105, "name": "porter"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160817091226MgQ83pyo6TldV274.jpg", "contents": "<h3><b>一些重要的新闻： </b></h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/financial/coty-income-dips-from-acquisition-expenses-10507408/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>日化巨头 Coty 集团计划出售或终止部分香水线</b></a> | Coty 计划剥离的这部分香水线，占据整个集团的香水事业部分 6%－8% 的净利润。据 Coty 的 CEO Bart Becht 称，集团将专注于那些高级品牌的香水，比如 Gucci、Hugo Boss、 Calvin Klein、Marc Jacobs 等。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/dicks-sporting-goods-earnings-10507418/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国体育用品零售连锁集团 Dick's Sporting Goods  第二季度股价大涨</b></a> |&nbsp;第二季度，Dick's Sporting Goods 的股票涨了 8%，至 59.6 美元每股，大大高于其市场预期。净利润上涨了 4.65%，至 9140 万美元。&nbsp;</p><p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/markets-news/designer-luxury/band-of-outsiders-new-york-fashion-week-clcc-scott-sternberg-10507416/\" rel=\"nofollow\">美国时尚新秀 Band of Outsiders 将重返纽约时装周</a></b> | 去年，Band of Outsiders 因为经济问题，放弃推出 2015 年秋季系列，并关闭了纽约旗舰店。近日，Band of Outsiders 宣布将于 9 月 11 日参加纽约时装周走秀，但它的创始人 Scott Sternberg 不会出席。</p><p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/legal/british-appeals-court-ruling-forces-isps-act-10506727/\" rel=\"nofollow\">英国法院维持 2014 年的裁决，强制关闭出售假冒商品的网站</a></b> | 该裁决是欧洲高级法院第一次彻底封锁出售假冒商品的网站，也被认为是历峰集团的一次胜利。据此判决，英国的五大网络服务商须封锁这个销售假冒卡地亚、万宝龙和万国表产品的网站。&nbsp;</p><h3><b>一些值得一看的： </b></h3><p>主打美式西海岸风格的日本街头品牌 FAT，创立于 2002 年，曾一度引领过日本街头风尚。此次推出了<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/fat-2016-aw-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\"> 2016 秋冬造型特辑</a>，包含了 Classic 经典、Sport 运动等支线。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817092256cR4oQ9AaVIlzGdEv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817092229c9Bm2lP7G0evgkzt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817092149eJmSQtaZ9kvVLP2n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817092237qxKIgLTehNsanpcw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817092247K2YL4QWpGaAP1rDq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>来自洛杉矶的时尚彩妆品牌 Urban Decay 推出全新眼影盘<a href=\"http://popbee.com/beauty/make-up/urban-decay-naked-ultimate-basics/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Naked Ultimate Basic</a>。这款眼影盘主打 Naked 裸妆主题，主打符合冬日的低调柔和的颜色。它一共有 12 个颜色，且全部都是 Urban Decay 从未有过的颜色。该眼影盘将于 9 月 18 日登陆美国 Urban Decay 官方网站。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817092315yFtnle0W3z4xZsmY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817092324sOqILCal5gozYKHh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817092333hw7ofTPVbILFNHGZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Porter 与日本设计公司 5525gallery 再度合作，推出了 2016 秋冬系列。<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/5525gallery-porter-suede-collection-fw-16\" rel=\"nofollow\">该系列主题为 Suede</a>，以高质量的麂皮打造出双肩包、腰包、手提包等单品。将于 8 月 19 日在 United Arrows &amp; Sons 原宿本店开售。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817092343QGzWqR14oKBpcHJX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817092351FJ05lf1Q8cRrH7DN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608170923590uIdWwCVO3sx2kn6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817092408MILNZoxHQGWjn57B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>英国女歌手 Rita Ora 再度与 Adidas Originals 合作，推出了<a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/fashion-news/adidas-originals-x-rita-ora/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> “queen of color, chaos and attitude” 系列</a>，通过不同色彩的碰撞，打造新鲜感。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817092421gR6SFhjTotf5ViUa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817092432zDuX4GnVBr2e3Nox.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817092446YnREZB49CcOoiVzX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817092446fcIoz1dPHRkAgLyT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817092459q9DbI8FQvanjWpE2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817092459486EoqcaGWMy9BKF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608170925100YNdaoyRtvsZTJr9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Louis Vuitton 将于今年 9 月推出全新 7 款香水系列，并邀请了 007 女郎 Lea Seydoux 担任代言人。这七款香水由大师级调香师 Jacques Cavallier-Belletru 调配，瓶身则由 Marc Newson 设计。七款香水分别为：Rose des Vents 风中玫瑰、Turbulences 湍流、Dans la Peau 沉醉、Apogee 巅峰、Contre Moi 依靠、Matière Noire 暗涌、Mille Feux 闪耀。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817093551U9CJ0r7KX4NhHkPY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608170934406OaNdKE7HL40hnUj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817093431hstb5EKkN4IDa1yJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817093511rPdKhyYCRWqF5QHw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817093512tCyM7uIgckj3Lro6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817093512dOBncmWr9GCugJK4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817093512e15vlUbMCVn6fwWu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817093512aQoG1Ayfm572xlJM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608170935126V4PUj53MBNmoszX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160817093537G5BTbxqoPNOZ04dm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}